00:14:50.079 --> 00:14:58.790
for a thousand years.

00:14:58.800 --> 00:15:07.269
People better get excited about it.

00:15:07.279 --> 00:15:11.189
I can't explain to you how green

00:15:11.199 --> 00:15:14.069
everything was.

00:15:14.079 --> 00:15:17.110
The grass and the trees and the bushes,

00:15:17.120 --> 00:15:20.629
there was no death.

00:15:20.639 --> 00:15:21.990
There was no death. Like, you know, you

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:24.389
see a dead limb here and there,

00:15:24.389 --> 00:15:24.399
outside—you

00:15:24.399 --> 00:15:26.069
go outside, there's a dead

00:15:26.079 --> 00:15:31.430
tree limb. There was no death. There

00:15:31.430 --> 00:15:31.440
were

00:15:31.440 --> 00:15:35.509
no dead brown leaves. Everything

00:15:35.519 --> 00:15:40.629
is alive and green.

00:15:40.639 --> 00:15:44.710
The sky is alive.

00:15:44.720 --> 00:15:50.470
The very atmosphere is alive.

00:15:50.480 --> 00:15:54.790
And even the grass was perfect.

00:15:54.800 --> 00:15:58.710
It was green, but it's thick, almost like

00:15:58.720 --> 00:16:01.509
you see that old Easter basket grass.

00:16:01.519 --> 00:16:03.189
How thick—I don't know how else to

00:16:03.199 --> 00:16:04.949
describe it to you. Like you'd see

00:16:04.959 --> 00:16:09.910
moss

00:16:09.920 --> 00:16:12.310
on trees.

00:16:12.320 --> 00:16:14.790
It's so thick, and like

00:16:14.800 --> 00:16:16.470
you could breathe it in and eat it,

00:16:16.480 --> 00:16:20.710
drink it, like the grass.

00:16:20.720 --> 00:16:25.110
Everything is so alive.

00:16:25.120 --> 00:16:27.110
And I could just look into it, but I

00:16:27.120 --> 00:16:29.269
was pulling back and I looked over here

00:16:29.279 --> 00:16:31.189
and I could see it. And as far as I

00:16:31.199 --> 00:16:34.150
could see, there was new.

00:16:34.160 --> 00:16:35.910
It was new, and it was beautiful, and

00:16:35.920 --> 00:16:39.350
pinks and yellows, and the sky was so

00:16:39.360 --> 00:16:42.069
alive.

00:16:42.079 --> 00:16:44.470
But it happened as a swirl above the

00:16:44.480 --> 00:16:46.949
atmosphere,

00:16:46.959 --> 00:16:50.629
you know, like a portal opened up,

00:16:50.639 --> 00:16:52.470
and all of a sudden this portal was

00:16:52.480 --> 00:16:54.870
turning, and all of a sudden it just came

00:16:54.880 --> 00:16:57.670
out of it, all this new, and it just

00:16:57.670 --> 00:16:57.680
transformed

00:16:57.680 --> 00:17:00.870
everything.

00:17:00.880 --> 00:17:02.790
But the portal was opened, and I could

00:17:02.800 --> 00:17:04.949
see it was like

00:17:04.949 --> 00:17:04.959
the

00:17:04.959 --> 00:17:07.990
size of a galaxy. It was massive. And

00:17:08.000 --> 00:17:09.990
all of a sudden, I saw this blue dot that

00:17:10.000 --> 00:17:12.230
looked like an Earth.

00:17:12.240 --> 00:17:13.990
It came out of it, and I thought it

00:17:14.000 --> 00:17:15.909
was an atom—like an atom,

00:17:15.919 --> 00:17:18.150
like you see

00:17:18.160 --> 00:17:20.630
particles. That's what I thought I was

00:17:20.640 --> 00:17:38.870
looking at. But it was something new.

00:17:38.880 --> 00:17:40.950
As I was praying about the King and all

00:17:40.960 --> 00:17:43.669
these other things,

00:17:43.679 --> 00:17:47.270
and I could see a scorpion's tail—I

00:17:47.270 --> 00:17:47.280
saw

00:17:47.280 --> 00:17:50.789
a scorpion. It was a part of that.

00:17:50.799 --> 00:17:52.390
And all of a sudden, I kept going and

00:17:52.400 --> 00:17:53.669
going. It was like I was going faster

00:17:53.679 --> 00:17:55.669
and faster. And I could see the King of

00:17:55.679 --> 00:17:59.190
England. And I could see there

00:17:59.200 --> 00:18:01.990
was so much demonic attached to that,

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:03.750
with the Illuminati and things like

00:18:03.760 --> 00:18:04.950
that. And I was in the Spirit, and I

00:18:04.960 --> 00:18:07.029
could see it, and it was pulling me.

00:18:11.919 --> 00:18:15.270
So, I gave you part of what happened

00:18:15.280 --> 00:18:18.070
that day when we prayed together.

00:18:19.919 --> 00:18:22.070
That was the part I wanted you to see,

00:18:22.080 --> 00:18:24.549
the end of it. He gave you a lot of

00:18:24.559 --> 00:18:26.390
the whole video, you know, about North

00:18:26.400 --> 00:18:28.710
Korea and all that.

00:18:28.720 --> 00:18:31.110
But I wanted you to hear what's

00:18:31.120 --> 00:18:34.150
coming, to give you some hope, to get you

00:18:34.160 --> 00:18:38.470
stirred up even more. When I go back

00:18:38.480 --> 00:18:41.270
over that and I'm hearing that again, it

00:18:41.280 --> 00:18:43.830
stirs me to intercede and start praying

00:18:43.840 --> 00:18:45.669
again.

00:18:45.679 --> 00:18:48.630
Folks, there's so much to look

00:18:48.640 --> 00:18:52.150
forward to:

00:18:52.160 --> 00:18:55.110
a new heaven, a new earth.

00:18:55.120 --> 00:18:56.789
Behold, He's going to make all things

00:18:56.799 --> 00:18:58.390
new.

00:18:58.400 --> 00:19:01.990
You know, I feel to talk about what

00:19:02.000 --> 00:19:07.909
happens after the rapture.

00:19:07.919 --> 00:19:10.390
I was praying one day,

00:19:10.400 --> 00:19:12.950
just like I always do, and I said,

00:19:12.960 --> 00:19:15.190
"Lord, how was Your day today?

00:19:15.200 --> 00:19:17.110
What went on in Your

00:19:17.110 --> 00:19:17.120
world?"You

00:19:17.120 --> 00:19:19.510
know, just trying to

00:19:19.520 --> 00:19:23.669
be as intimate as I can with Him. "Hey, how

00:19:23.669 --> 00:19:23.679
are

00:19:23.679 --> 00:19:27.430
things going?"You know, I talk to

00:19:27.440 --> 00:19:30.390
God like I talk to my son or my wife.

00:19:30.400 --> 00:19:32.630
I'm not religious.

00:19:32.640 --> 00:19:35.510
I just talk to Him like He is right

00:19:35.520 --> 00:19:38.070
here, an ever-present help in a time of

00:19:38.080 --> 00:19:40.870
need, because He's my friend.

00:19:40.880 --> 00:19:44.710
And I said, "How are things going

00:19:44.710 --> 00:19:44.720
today?"And

00:19:44.720 --> 00:19:46.470
He said, "Brendon, I'll show you

00:19:46.480 --> 00:19:48.470
what we're doing today."And if you want

00:19:48.480 --> 00:19:49.990
to believe this, fine. If you don't,

00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:51.669
fine. It was real to me, and it's what

00:19:51.679 --> 00:19:55.270
happened. All of a sudden, a

00:19:55.280 --> 00:19:58.950
portal opened up above me, and He

00:19:58.960 --> 00:20:00.710
allowed me to come up through it, and He

00:20:00.720 --> 00:20:03.029
said, "We're getting ready for your

00:20:03.039 --> 00:20:05.190
return."And

00:20:05.200 --> 00:20:08.470
I saw a banquet table. There

00:20:08.470 --> 00:20:08.480
were

00:20:08.480 --> 00:20:11.029
tables all around

00:20:11.039 --> 00:20:14.070
for the Marriage Supper of the Lamb, for

00:20:14.080 --> 00:20:16.630
a banquet, a rehearsal. It was a wedding

00:20:16.640 --> 00:20:20.230
feast. It was like a beautiful

00:20:20.240 --> 00:20:22.070
reception.

00:20:22.080 --> 00:20:24.710
Everybody's plates were

00:20:24.720 --> 00:20:27.590
perfect. Some of them looked like lilies,

00:20:27.600 --> 00:20:29.750
but they were transparent, beautiful

00:20:29.760 --> 00:20:33.990
glass plates and china and silverware.

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:36.390
Beautiful, beautiful

00:20:36.390 --> 00:20:36.400
place

00:20:36.400 --> 00:20:39.590
settings. And each one of them—some of

00:20:39.600 --> 00:20:42.710
them had chopsticks on them, some of

00:20:42.720 --> 00:20:46.149
them weren't like nice silverware, some

00:20:46.159 --> 00:20:48.549
of them had chopsticks

00:20:48.559 --> 00:20:51.029
depending on your culture.

00:20:51.039 --> 00:20:54.070
He honored the culture of the person.

00:20:54.080 --> 00:20:57.029
But every single one of them had a

00:20:57.029 --> 00:20:57.039
place

00:20:57.039 --> 00:20:59.029
setting of your name. There was a

00:20:59.039 --> 00:21:00.870
name on the plate, and it had your

00:21:00.870 --> 00:21:00.880
reserved

00:21:00.880 --> 00:21:05.909
seat on your plate. Behind was a

00:21:05.919 --> 00:21:08.710
beautiful chair that was carved out

00:21:08.710 --> 00:21:08.720
of

00:21:08.720 --> 00:21:11.190
some kind of beautiful wood. It was the

00:21:11.200 --> 00:21:13.750
most beautiful chair I've ever seen

00:21:13.760 --> 00:21:15.350
before.

00:21:15.360 --> 00:21:17.510
All of the flowers were draping it, and

00:21:17.520 --> 00:21:20.549
it was all set up perfectly to celebrate

00:21:20.559 --> 00:21:23.110
your coming.

00:21:23.120 --> 00:21:25.510
There's a reception coming, a

00:21:25.520 --> 00:21:27.750
reception that He has for you as we

00:21:27.760 --> 00:21:31.669
cross over. The tables,

00:21:31.679 --> 00:21:33.830
the doilies, and the

00:21:33.840 --> 00:21:37.190
beautiful white linen were all on this

00:21:37.200 --> 00:21:40.470
table. The tablecloth was

00:21:40.480 --> 00:21:43.110
all like lace, like somebody had

00:21:43.120 --> 00:21:45.830
crocheted it. It was a beautiful place, and

00:21:45.840 --> 00:21:48.710
the way the table was

00:21:48.720 --> 00:21:51.270
decorated with the most beautiful

00:21:51.280 --> 00:21:53.830
flowers that were alive with

00:21:53.830 --> 00:21:53.840
fragrances—they

00:21:53.840 --> 00:21:55.830
were in these

00:21:55.840 --> 00:21:58.789
vases that were all on these tables

00:21:58.799 --> 00:22:01.830
as far as the eye could see.

00:22:01.840 --> 00:22:04.710
Then I could see tulle. There was

00:22:04.710 --> 00:22:04.720
big—you

00:22:04.720 --> 00:22:07.350
know how you go down in the South, in

00:22:07.360 --> 00:22:09.909
like the Louisiana area, and they have the

00:22:09.919 --> 00:22:12.310
moss on them. When we went to

00:22:12.320 --> 00:22:15.750
Florida, they had greenery growing on

00:22:15.760 --> 00:22:17.350
the trees that looked kind of like

00:22:17.360 --> 00:22:20.549
moss, but it was

00:22:20.559 --> 00:22:24.149
dangling off the trees down in Florida.

00:22:24.159 --> 00:22:26.310
And so much so that when I saw it,

00:22:26.320 --> 00:22:27.669
I stopped and pulled the car over

00:22:27.679 --> 00:22:29.510
because I said, "I've seen that in

00:22:29.510 --> 00:22:29.520
heaven."When

00:22:29.520 --> 00:22:32.390
the Lord allowed me to, I

00:22:32.400 --> 00:22:34.470
pulled over, and I broke some off the

00:22:34.480 --> 00:22:35.909
trees so I could touch it, because

00:22:35.919 --> 00:22:38.470
up in Oklahoma, we don't have

00:22:38.480 --> 00:22:40.789
that,

00:22:40.799 --> 00:22:42.470
and I've never seen that or felt it

00:22:42.480 --> 00:22:45.110
before. And it felt soft.

00:22:45.120 --> 00:22:46.549
But when I saw it in heaven, it was

00:22:46.559 --> 00:22:48.549
draping off the trees. But there was

00:22:48.559 --> 00:22:51.350
beautiful tulle, beautiful

00:22:51.360 --> 00:22:54.149
white tulle and stuff wrapped in the

00:22:54.159 --> 00:22:57.190
trees with twinkle lights all inside of

00:22:57.190 --> 00:22:57.200
them—beautiful

00:22:57.200 --> 00:23:00.710
lights,

00:23:00.720 --> 00:23:02.870
lighting the trees that were draping

00:23:02.880 --> 00:23:06.070
over the tables.

00:23:06.080 --> 00:23:09.669
And there were flowers beyond

00:23:09.679 --> 00:23:11.590
human comprehension. There were flowers

00:23:11.600 --> 00:23:13.750
all around on these tables: white

00:23:13.760 --> 00:23:16.390
flowers, yellow flowers, red flowers.

00:23:16.400 --> 00:23:19.110
Beautiful reception.

00:23:19.120 --> 00:23:21.029
And all of it was being prepared for

00:23:21.039 --> 00:23:22.549
every single one of us. And your name

00:23:22.559 --> 00:23:24.789
tag was on your plates, like I said. And

00:23:24.799 --> 00:23:26.630
I could see my name tag. I could see my

00:23:26.640 --> 00:23:29.430
wife's. I could see every single one of

00:23:29.440 --> 00:23:31.669
these places that were made for every

00:23:31.679 --> 00:23:33.909
single one of us. And it was all by our

00:23:33.919 --> 00:23:36.070
heart's desire.

00:23:36.080 --> 00:23:37.750
Whatever is inside of you, what you're

00:23:37.760 --> 00:23:40.230
believing for, the greatest expectation,

00:23:40.240 --> 00:23:42.070
ladies and gentlemen, God has it inside

00:23:42.080 --> 00:23:43.669
there, and He's going to bring it to

00:23:43.679 --> 00:23:48.549
pass. Watch. And as I saw

00:23:48.559 --> 00:23:51.110
they were getting over to the side, I

00:23:51.120 --> 00:23:53.430
could see Jesus and he was riding on a

00:23:53.440 --> 00:23:55.909
white horse.

00:23:55.919 --> 00:23:59.190
There was jewels all on the side of this

00:23:59.200 --> 00:24:02.390
horse's bridle, all around his ears.

00:24:02.400 --> 00:24:04.470
And it was jewels. The most beautiful

00:24:04.470 --> 00:24:04.480
jewels—the

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:08.149
world in all the

00:24:08.159 --> 00:24:11.350
finest jewelry stores that

00:24:11.360 --> 00:24:14.230
you've ever seen cannot compare to what

00:24:14.240 --> 00:24:16.070
I saw. The massive diamonds and the

00:24:16.080 --> 00:24:19.110
rubies and the sapphires, the beautiful

00:24:19.120 --> 00:24:21.190
splendor of heaven and the jewelry

00:24:21.200 --> 00:24:24.310
around this horse's

00:24:24.310 --> 00:24:24.320
bridle.

00:24:24.320 --> 00:24:26.390
He was up there just like he always is

00:24:26.400 --> 00:24:28.950
with that beautiful cloak on.

00:24:28.960 --> 00:24:32.310
His crown has a

00:24:32.320 --> 00:24:34.870
beautiful black and white

00:24:34.870 --> 00:24:34.880
embroidery

00:24:34.880 --> 00:24:36.630
around it

00:24:36.640 --> 00:24:38.950
with purple on top and jewels all over

00:24:38.960 --> 00:24:42.390
his crown. His cape has purple and

00:24:42.400 --> 00:24:44.789
it has this black and white thing

00:24:44.799 --> 00:24:47.110
that I saw around it. And it has this

00:24:47.120 --> 00:24:49.830
tassel that buttons it up here

00:24:49.840 --> 00:24:52.549
that's all fine jewelry and it's

00:24:52.549 --> 00:24:52.559
handcrafted.

00:24:52.559 --> 00:24:55.909
It's gorgeous. Gorgeous, the

00:24:55.919 --> 00:24:57.990
way that the stuff goes around

00:24:58.000 --> 00:25:00.549
his cloak.

00:25:00.559 --> 00:25:03.350
And he was riding on the

00:25:03.350 --> 00:25:03.360
horse

00:25:03.360 --> 00:25:05.029
and I could see on these streets of

00:25:05.039 --> 00:25:06.710
gold, there was the most beautiful

00:25:06.720 --> 00:25:08.950
streets of gold. And he was riding down

00:25:08.960 --> 00:25:11.669
this street, but

00:25:11.679 --> 00:25:14.390
there was people with banners that were

00:25:14.400 --> 00:25:17.190
on the side of the street that had 'King

00:25:17.200 --> 00:25:20.390
of Kings and Lord of Lords'all on the

00:25:20.400 --> 00:25:21.909
side of these banners. And they were dripping

00:25:21.909 --> 00:25:21.919
in

00:25:21.919 --> 00:25:24.470
purple, the most beautiful,

00:25:24.480 --> 00:25:26.470
brilliant purple I've ever seen with

00:25:26.480 --> 00:25:28.710
gold all around them. And they had

00:25:28.720 --> 00:25:30.710
the staffs and they were standing on

00:25:30.720 --> 00:25:32.549
the side of the street and there were

00:25:32.559 --> 00:25:37.510
people of all kinds from all kinds of

00:25:37.520 --> 00:25:39.190
generations is what I'm going to say.

00:25:39.200 --> 00:25:41.350
The way they looked,

00:25:41.360 --> 00:25:44.310
on this side of the street there were what

00:25:44.310 --> 00:25:44.320
looked

00:25:44.320 --> 00:25:47.190
like English style

00:25:47.200 --> 00:25:50.710
homes that were cobblestone with

00:25:50.720 --> 00:25:53.190
beautiful roofs.

00:25:53.200 --> 00:25:55.990
It looked like something out

00:25:56.000 --> 00:25:59.110
of medieval times, but it

00:25:59.120 --> 00:26:01.909
was all perfect, the way all the grout

00:26:01.919 --> 00:26:04.230
and all the stuff was on these buildings

00:26:04.240 --> 00:26:06.070
as I can remember it even still like

00:26:06.080 --> 00:26:07.510
today, I can quote it back to you

00:26:07.520 --> 00:26:09.190
perfectly.

00:26:09.200 --> 00:26:12.310
But as he was riding down, I could hear

00:26:12.320 --> 00:26:16.470
instruments playing music that was so

00:26:16.480 --> 00:26:19.029
beautiful, beyond anything I can describe

00:26:19.039 --> 00:26:22.630
to you. And they were playing behind

00:26:22.640 --> 00:26:24.789
him and they were having a parade. They

00:26:24.799 --> 00:26:27.029
were parading

00:26:27.039 --> 00:26:29.029
on this gold street and they were

00:26:29.039 --> 00:26:32.070
saying, 'For he is good and his mercy

00:26:32.080 --> 00:26:36.070
endures forever; for the Lord, he is good

00:26:36.080 --> 00:26:39.669
and his mercy endures forever.'And they

00:26:39.679 --> 00:26:41.190
were shouting and you could hear it and

00:26:41.200 --> 00:26:43.190
it was echoing all throughout the land.

00:26:43.200 --> 00:26:44.710
I could hear it in heaven. It was

00:26:44.720 --> 00:26:46.630
echoing and it was almost

00:26:46.640 --> 00:26:50.070
deafening how loud it was: 'For the Lord,

00:26:50.080 --> 00:26:53.029
he is good and his mercy endures

00:26:53.029 --> 00:26:53.039
forever.'And

00:26:53.039 --> 00:26:55.029
they were saying it and

00:26:55.039 --> 00:26:56.870
they just kept saying it.

00:26:56.880 --> 00:26:59.190
And I could see this like confetti in

00:26:59.200 --> 00:27:01.350
the air.

00:27:01.360 --> 00:27:03.669
It was like beautiful stuff flying in

00:27:03.679 --> 00:27:06.310
the air all around. It was being kept

00:27:06.320 --> 00:27:09.430
all as he was marching in on his

00:27:09.440 --> 00:27:11.350
horse.

00:27:11.360 --> 00:27:14.789
They were preparing for us to come.

00:27:14.799 --> 00:27:17.350
And I could hear, 'For the Lord, he is good

00:27:17.360 --> 00:27:21.510
and his mercy endures

00:27:21.510 --> 00:27:21.520
forever.'And

00:27:21.520 --> 00:27:23.830
at the end of the road, I could see

00:27:23.840 --> 00:27:27.909
this massive castle

00:27:27.919 --> 00:27:30.149
that had the most beautiful sides. It

00:27:30.159 --> 00:27:32.310
was a massive castle, but there was a

00:27:32.320 --> 00:27:36.149
bridge and on this bridge I could see,

00:27:36.159 --> 00:27:38.390
going through here, I could see a stream,

00:27:38.400 --> 00:27:40.549
but on the other side of the bridge, it

00:27:40.559 --> 00:27:42.310
was the most beautiful trees and the

00:27:42.320 --> 00:27:44.470
most beautiful green grass. And there

00:27:44.480 --> 00:27:46.870
was a beautiful—all up here—a massive

00:27:46.880 --> 00:27:49.110
castle on a hill, and I still don't know

00:27:49.120 --> 00:27:50.630
what that castle is, but I'm telling you,

